{"tid":694881,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 SSD無啦啦跳至100%使用率","createTime":"2018-06-08T17:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T17:11:10.000Z","uid":73715,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"75abc2672e23ceb602393d716511d86e7d184855","tid":694881,"uid":73715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T17:30:37.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟自從砌左新機之後就KEEP住有畫面定格既問題<br />\n就算開住佢放係到乜都唔做都係無啦啦畫面凍結<br />\n岩岩開住工作管理員由佢放係到乜都唔做<br />\nCHECK左發現係SSD突然跳到100%使用率<br />\n之後畫面就凍結左 有時有鼠標係到 有時無埋鼠標<br />\n其他硬件依然係工作管理員到見到係正常運作<br />\n<br />\n部電腦既SPEC如下：<br />\nCPU：AMD RYZEN 3 2200G<br />\nMother Board：Asrock AB350M-Pro4<br />\nRam：Crucial 8GB DDR4-2400 兩條<br />\nSSD：Transcend SSD220S 240GB<br />\nPOWER：Corsair CX450<br />\n<br />\n我上網睇過其他用家<br />\n用同一塊板同RYZEN CPU都有相同問題<br />\n唔知各位巴打有無高見可以教路一下"},{"pid":"f238c07f51aaf82af0559641f092304ca77339f8","tid":694881,"uid":53857,"like":27,"dislike":5,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T17:36:55.000Z","msg":"鼠標<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612a4d1e548e8ad6c56809af0f1ffde22ed8b8fa","tid":694881,"uid":26003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T17:44:08.000Z","msg":"掘礦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4d30a388ad90d9d6e617ecf96707182a363132","tid":694881,"uid":1085,"like":22,"dislike":4,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T21:53:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0440d2a29d927967337b84e62ea84ef3ab2417af","tid":694881,"uid":36478,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"75abc2672e23ceb602393d716511d86e7d184855","tid":694881,"uid":73715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T17:30:37.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟自從砌左新機之後就KEEP住有畫面定格既問題<br />\n就算開住佢放係到乜都唔做都係無啦啦畫面凍結<br />\n岩岩開住工作